{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cryptica is a narrative-based psychological horror game where the apocalypse is only the beginning. Explore the enigmatic lands of Antarctica and its surrounding areas while the world ends.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886380/extras/6.gif?t=1726845351\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play as Ari Harper, as he desperately attempts to find his missing sister, who has disappeared with a film crew while making a documentary about the area. Uncover unfathomable horrors, discover ancestral secrets, and find your sister at all costs.  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Player Freedom</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Players can explore in 1st or 3rd person modes in massive rustic and surreal environments. This game has no locked doors or blocked paths to slow you down. Go forth, and explore freely.\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886380/extras/ezgif.com-optimize__2_.gif?t=1726845351\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Psychological Uncertainty </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unprecedented permafrost melt has given life to a new fungus in your exploration area. This fungus can emit airborne spores that can cause auditory and visual hallucinations. Embrace or reject this mechanic at your leisure. You decide what\u2019s real and what\u2019s imagination.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886380/extras/4.gif?t=1726845351\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Heavy Lore</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are pieces of this mystery scattered all around you. This place has a dark and complex history, diligent exploration will reward players with valuable knowledge and context to the cosmic horrors around you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886380/extras/1.gif?t=1726845351\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Gameplay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>EXPLORE</strong> abandoned mines, desolate whaling outposts, and ancient archeological sites. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>INTERACT</strong> with locals and other characters in the area for insight into the missing film crew.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>OBSERVE inter-dimensional beings, ghosts, henchmen, and ancient cryptids.  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886380/extras/3.gif?t=1726845351\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886380/extras/2.gif?t=1726845351\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>3-5 Hours Gameplay</strong></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886380/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1726845351","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886380/page.bg.jpg?t=1726845351","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886380/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1726845351","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886380/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1726845351","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":"This game contains scenes with disturbing imagery and explores themes of existential dread. The use of hallucinogenic substances is depicted. "},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cryptica is a narrative-based psychological horror game where the apocalypse is only the